'''''Leena''''' was an [[Action VI bulk transport/Legends|Action VI bulk transport]] that carried [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] dancers of the ''[[Dunari's Rest]]'' when the latter was attacked by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces. It made it to [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] intact thanks to assistance from the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

